#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.67:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.67:0.2"
msgid "7. Bodhipakkhiyavagga"
msgstr "7. Leading to Awakening"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.67:0.3"
msgid "67. Paṭhamarukkhasutta"
msgstr "67. A Tree (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.67:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci jambudīpakā rukkhā, jambū tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, of all the trees in India, the rose-apple is said to be the "
"best."

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāya."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the "
"qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened."

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.3"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyā dhammā?"
msgstr "And what are the qualities that lead to awakening?"

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.4"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ, bhikkhave, bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "The faculties of faith,"

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.5"
msgid "Vīriyindriyaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "energy,"

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.6"
msgid "satindriyaṃ …"
msgstr "mindfulness,"

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.7"
msgid "samādhindriyaṃ …"
msgstr "immersion,"

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.8"
msgid "paññindriyaṃ bodhipakkhiyo dhammo, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr ""
"and wisdom are qualities that lead to awakening, in that they lead to "
"becoming awakened."

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.9"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ye keci jambudīpakā rukkhā, jambū tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati;"
msgstr "Of all the trees in India, the rose-apple is said to be the best."

msgctxt "sn48.67:1.10"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci bodhipakkhiyā dhammā, paññindriyaṃ tesaṃ "
"aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the "
"qualities that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.67:1.11"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
